    "**My Location** - Toggle on/off and choose position (Before or After city list)" : {

    },
    "**Name (A–Z)** — Default alphabetical order" : {

    },
    "**Name (Z–A)** — Reverse alphabetical" : {

    },
    "**Narrow (10°)** - Precise tracking, 17 miles wide at 100 miles" : {

    },
    "**Navigate Cities** - Swipe up for cities farther away, swipe down for closer cities" : {

    },
    "**Navigating Through Dates:**" : {

    },
    "**North to South** — Cities ordered from highest to lowest latitude" : {

    },
    "**Note:** Marine forecast data is available for coastal locations. Inland cities may show limited or no marine data. Sea Level Height (tidal data) is enabled by default and shown first in the marine section." : {

    },
    "**Note:** My Location never appears in your saved city list unless you explicitly choose \"Add to My City List\". It will not show up in iCloud sync, widgets, or Weather in Time comparisons unless added." : {

