    "Tap 'Load History' to view" : {

    },
    "Tap **Add Widget**, then drag it to the position you want" : {

    },
    "Tap any direction to explore cities along that path. For example, tap \"North\" to see all cities north of your location." : {

    },
    "Tap the **+** button in the top-left corner to open the widget gallery" : {

    },
    "Tap the **City** row to open the picker" : {

